<p>-e-<hi rend='Italic'><foreign>Carcajada</foreign></hi></p>
<p>Ah, ah, ah, ah, ah, ah, ah, ah,</p>
<p>Nola guk dakusgun gaur.</p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>DON DIEGO </hi><foreign><hi rend='Italic'>(representa)</hi></foreign></p>
<p><foreign> &#191;Qu&eacute; es eso? &#191;Te has vuelto loco?</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>DON ANTONIO</hi></p>
<p><foreign> Vengan Vmds., por Dios,</foreign></p>
<p><foreign> Que es la cosa m&aacute;s graciosa </foreign></p>
